data.description: Don’t miss this phenomenal LIKE NEW 4 bed, 2.5 bath home in the desirable Towns @ Riverfront Community! NEW interior paint and carpet. The open floorplan is perfect: on the main level you get engineered hardwoods, high ceilings, kitchen w/granite countertops, SS appliances, large island, walk-in pantry, large dining space, and living room w/gas fireplace. Upper level holds the primary bed with private bath, two additional bedrooms & laundry w/washer & dryer included. Downstairs is the 4th BR or potential office with access to backyard. The Towns @ Riverfront offers trails along the river to Lowell park boat launch! Direct access to I5/HWY 2 & 2 mins to train/bus station, future light rail & upcoming Riverfront Town Center!
